ActSpecies at Risk Act
SubjectOrder Amending Schedule 1 to the Species at Risk Act
PrecisOrder Amending SCHEDULE 1 TO THE SPECIES AT RISK ACT in order to add three bat species (the Little Brown Myotis, the Tri-colored Bat and the Northern Myotis) which are facing imminent threats to their survival and recovery.
